Name:
 Imperial AP-2 Attack Droid
Model:
 Armored Platform-2
Information:
 The AP-2 Attack Droid is the cornerstone of the Empire´s new
 anti-infantry assault droid team. Equipped with rapid-fire light
 repeating blasters on a rotating ´head turret´ and independently
 rotating heavy blaster rifles, the AP-2 is capable of single-
 handedly taking on nearly a whole squad of Republic soldiers.
 A pair of micro-grenade launchers installed in the lower arms
 round out the AP-2´s weaponry.
Photo:
