Name:
 Imperial AP-3 Attack Droid
Model:
 Assault Platform-3
Information:
 The Imperial AP-3 Attack Droid looks like an astromech droid
 equipped with missile racks. The AP-3 unit trationally has a rear
 assault postion and uses its assault rockets and micro-proton-
 torpedos to blast vehicles and large numbers of enemy troops.
 While it is slow when moving on its wheeled legs, a repulsorlift
 drive unit at the base of its body allows it to move across the
 battlefield when summoned by AP-1-C Attack Droids.
